      <akn:section eId="sec_6_501">
        <akn:num>6-501</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Review of building permit applications; design and construction requirements.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_6-501_1">
      <akn:num>(1)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Be designed (or modified) and anchored to prevent flotation, collapse, or lateral movement of the structure;</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_6-501_2">
      <akn:num>(2)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Use construction materials and utility equipment that are resistant to flood damage; and</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_6-501_3">
      <akn:num>(3)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Use construction methods and practices that will minimize flood damage.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
